column5: Great vid!  Although I think the fish might have suffered a brain injury, lol.
Which way do I go, which way do i go.... Poor bugger was so confused... Glad they got him out , both times..LOL
stupid fish, must have been a member of Green Piece
The operator of the ROV really knows his stuff.He did a bang up job
Cool video, poor thing.  I like the comment "I wonder how many quarters he put in the claw machine before he got the prize?"
Amazing video...but when that thing swam right back in to get stuck a second time, I think I'd be adding the harpoon attachment to the claw and serving up fresh marlin steak for dinner
I like the comment "I wonder how many quarters he put in the claw machine before he got the prize?"   LOL!!!
I'm pretty sure that was a swordfish. I wonder how long it was stuck in there before they realized it??
I guess they removed it so it wouldn't damage wires with its bill. Or did they remove it to save its life? Regardless great video and nice work removing it.
How did they even know that fish was stuck down there ??? Good job of getting it free though.
